<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٧٧١ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/13865">‌يُونُسُ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2594">‌أَبُو دَاوُدَ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٧٣⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">‌شُعْبَةُ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">‌قَتَادَةَ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2436">‌سَعِيدِ بْنِ الْمُسَيِّبِ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3732">‌ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ </a>،<span class="c5"> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«الْعَائِدُ فِي هِبَتِهِ كَالْعَائِدِ فِي قَيْئِهِ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>